name: KA-DOING! Abnormality Pack - Green/Pink Variant
description: This is the first time "Fish Boy" has been featured as a Boxy Mouse product, and this one is a doozy (and quite abnormal). The first part of this pack is a 11" x 6" die-cut sticker sheet -- hand screen-printed on glossy vinyl. The second item is a handsome custom framed screen print on glossy stock. As if that weren't enough, the funtime is topped off with a lovely package of two 1" magnets and two 1" buttons. All these items were printed/framed/manufactured at Boxy Mouse Design Studio (and laundry room). This is a limited edition package -- only 5 are available.

name: Deluxe Magnets (medium sized)
description: These are manufactured out of 1/4" rigid plastic (Sintra) and were screen printed at Boxy Mouse Design Studio (and laundry room). They measure approximately 2.25"x2.75". The magnet is quite strong, and they are weatherproof. Please choose which character with the drop-down menu below.

name: Youth Corruption Sticker Pack (small)
description: Each pack contains 5 small vinyl stickers (1.75" square), each with a different color. These stickers were printed, die-cut and packaged at Boxy Mouse Design Studio (and laundry room). It is possible that these items may not corrupt youths. Then again...

name: Framed Vending Machine Screen Print #1
description: This is the same print that is been used in the "Boxy Mouse Button Dispensary" vending machines during 2012. Hand-printed and framed at Boxy Mouse Design Studio (and laundry room). Framed size is 8"x11". Choose your color with the drop-down menu below.

name: Framed VALUCO Screen Print
description: A print inspired by the VALUCO typeface. Please note the fluorescent colors are super-hot and bright, and impossible to photograph properly. Hand-printed and framed at Boxy Mouse Design Studio (and laundry room). Framed size is 11"x11". Choose your color with the drop-down menu below.

name: Sticker Slap Pack #1
description: Four 3" x 4" vinyl stickers (2 "Incognito" & 2 "4-Eyes") are included in this pack. Also, a bonus plain Boxy Mouse sticker will be included with each slap pack order.

name: Boxy Mouse Street Magnet
description: These are scaled-down versions of the pieces that are infesting the streets of Minneapolis and St. Paul this year. They are made out of 1/4" rigid plastic (Sintra) and graphic vinyl and measure 2.5"x3". The magnet is quite strong, and they are weatherproof. Please choose Plain or Incognito Mouse with the drop-down menu below.

name: Boxy Mouse Stickers
description: Each pack contains 3 vinyl stickers. Each measures 2.125" x 2.75". Price includes shipping.

name: Super Boxy Funtime Magnet Pack
description: Now you can make your own Super Boxy Funtime Maggnet Pack! Go to the Super Boxy Funtime Button Library and pick out three designs you like. Enter the numbers into the "Note to seller" section during your PayPal checkout and they'll be put into a pack and shipped out. Or, you can be more general -- like "all green" or "Jellyfish" -- and they will be picked for you. Vive le Boxy Mouse!

name: Super Boxy Funtime Button Pack
description: Now you can make your own Super Boxy Funtime Button Pack! Go to the Super Boxy Funtime Button Library and pick out four designs you like.
